    "description": "FPV LOGIC是一款FPV无人机模拟器,全力打造的物理引擎无限接近无人机真实的飞行状态,能够带来接近真实无人机的操作体验,并且拥有真实无人机无法实现的众多功能.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398030/extras/d24c91d03da4ec604f69647a3e7af736.poster.avif?t=1749571580\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398030/extras/d24c91d03da4ec604f69647a3e7af736.webm?t=1749571580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398030/extras/d24c91d03da4ec604f69647a3e7af736.mp4?t=1749571580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>体验来自不同厂商的各种FPV无人机,从机架到螺旋桨,从重量到性能,每一款无人机都会带来不同的细腻操作体验,三种不同视角能够随时切换以让你从不同视角体验飞行乐趣.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398030/extras/acb04142bb3beb728a2041bd8e7ae85a.poster.avif?t=1749571580\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398030/extras/acb04142bb3beb728a2041bd8e7ae85a.webm?t=1749571580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398030/extras/acb04142bb3beb728a2041bd8e7ae85a.mp4?t=1749571580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>无论你喜欢自由花式飞行还是专业竞速,或者仅仅是用微型无人机悠闲的飞行,你都能在FPV LOGIC中找到乐趣,为花式飞行精心设计的地图能满足你提升飞行技巧的一切需要,专业比赛规格的竞速赛道加上最多20架AI无人机一起和你飚速度,绝对能让你置身比赛现场.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398030/extras/df1adee99deb646ae45e677b76cbe803.poster.avif?t=1749571580\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398030/extras/df1adee99deb646ae45e677b76cbe803.webm?t=1749571580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398030/extras/df1adee99deb646ae45e677b76cbe803.mp4?t=1749571580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>简化的无人机各种参数设计让FPV新手也能自在飞行,如果你是专业飞手同样也能轻松调整你的无人机至最佳状态.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398030/extras/a14f6f1fdd78712faa37f512d631931d.poster.avif?t=1749571580\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398030/extras/a14f6f1fdd78712faa37f512d631931d.webm?t=1749571580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398030/extras/a14f6f1fdd78712faa37f512d631931d.mp4?t=1749571580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>FPV LOGIC支持Windows识别的任何遥控器和游戏手柄,强烈建议使用无人机遥控器获得最佳操作体验.",
